    "created_at": "2015-10-16T07:14:44Z",
    "updated_at": "2015-10-16T07:14:44Z",
    "body": "I ended by having two `desktop` apps and using [inter-process communication](https://github.com/IonicaBizau/node-messager): if I want to keep A in the bottom (always), I catch the `focus` event of A and send an event to B which focuses the B window. Not sure if this is the best way, but it's working. :tada: \n"
